# NOTICE — two-GAN field detection model

This folder contains code vendored from:
  https://github.com/lood339/pytorch-two-GAN

Specifically a fork preserved at:
  https://github.com/AB25217/pytorch-two-GAN

Original paper:
  Chen, J. & Little, J.J. (2019)
  "Sports Camera Calibration via Synthetic Data"
  CVPR Workshops. arXiv:1810.10658

Files vendored:
  - networks.py (UnetGenerator + define_G — used for inference)

Only the inference-time components are vendored. Training-time utilities
(visualizer, options, dataset loaders) are not included because they are
not used by this project.

